            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli tlen moixtlapaltlalia zo ce tlamantli xitlahuac, nochipa motequihuia para ce achi tlalli tlen ixtlehcolez zo ixtemoles, calaqui ce achi tlalli tlen moixnezcayotihtoc quence ixtlehcolez zo ixtemolez quence tlen mochiuhtoc icelti zo tlachihualli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
